Looking at the curl test I did earlier, the search API returns data in this format:
```json
{
  "query": {
    "searchinfo": {"totalhits": 5797},
    "search": [
      {
        "ns": 0,
        "title": "Logs",
        "pageid": 10005,
        "size": 8888,
        "wordcount": 600,
        "snippet": "<span class=\"searchmatch\">Logs</span>...",
        "timestamp": "2025-08-05T21:45:40Z"
      }
    ]
  }
}
```

This is different from the current generator approach which returns pages in a "pages" array. I need to create new models that match this structure.

Let me create the SearchApiResponse models first.

